Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:24.56,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:39.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:52.42,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.42,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.73,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:06.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艷麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:13.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.38,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:24.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
